Some Hadiths related to the Asmaul Husna:

- Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) said, "Allah has ninety-nine names, one hundred minus one. Whoever memorizes them will enter Paradise." (Sahih Bukhari)

- Abu Hurairah (may Allah be pleased with him) reported that the Prophet (peace be upon him) said, "Allah's most beautiful name is Al-Hayy Al-Qayyum." (Sahih Muslim)
